name: Inverted Cross Samsung Galaxy S3 Case
description:
- Brand new, high quality case.

- Will protect your phone from bumps, scratches, dust, and dings.

- Lightweight and durable.

- Snap style case. Easy to put on and remove.

- High gloss scratch resistant finish.

- Allows use of all of your function buttons, and recharge port.

- Will fit on all Samsung Galaxy S3 models.

- Image is imbedded into case using the Heat Transfer Dye Sublimation process. Scratch resistant.
